title: Episode 60: Super-Villains on the Couch (with Bryan Carr and Chuck Rybak)
itunes:author: UW-Green Bay Psychology Department
itunes:summary: This special LIVE episode was part of the Brown County Library's 3rd annual Comic-Con! In this cross-over episode our host, Ryan Martin, joins forces with Bryan Carr from Serious Fun and Dr. Chuck Rybak to talk about some of your favorite super-villains. Listen in as they discuss the psychology, mental health, and background of super-villains such as Lex Luthor, Killmonger, and the infamous pairing of the Joker and Harley Quinn!
